\f0\fs24 \cf0 # SIEM Threat Detection Lab (Azure + Windows VM)\
\
## \uc0\u55357 \u56524  Project Overview\
This project demonstrates how a Security Information and Event Management (SIEM) system detects and analyzes successful login activity using Windows Security Event Logs.\
\
The goal of this lab is to simulate real-world SOC analyst tasks such as:\
- Monitoring authentication events\
- Identifying successful logons\
- Understanding how SIEM tools detect and correlate security activity\
\
This project was completed using Microsoft Azure, a Windows Virtual Machine, and Windows Security Event Logs.\
\
